Title: Magical holiday
Name: Ooze
Date: Dec 23

A magical holiday

The twinkling lights
Shining so beutiful and bright
What a wounderful site to see
A beutiful trimmed Christmas tree
On Christmas day
Just makes it a magical holiday

Children sitting on santa's lap Dreaming about the presents they will unwrap
Girls and boys
Opening their toys
On Christmas day
Just makes it a magical holiday

Lovers kissing under the mistletoe
the fresh blanket of new fallen snow
On Christmas day
Just makes it a very Magical holiday

(C) 1996 David Howard aka Ooze aka Oozork

Ooze

HAPPY HOLIDAY!!!




